imisstrishandthatisall.

i hate waking up in the morning and regretting everything i did the night before...

and it has been happening so much lately.

i hadn't written in my other livejournal in over a year, but thanks to tryshthedishYEA, i made another one.
i realize how much i missed writing in these things when i'm bored, depressed, being stupid, etc.

summer is over. how sad.

i like hanging out with ashpea, trysh, tee, george, and jman.
i like going to parties at trysh's house and regretting everything i did the next morning.
i like eating at applebees at least two or three times a week.
i like boys i don't know stripping for my birthday.
i like going to greg jorz's house and seeing people i haven't seen since grade school.
i like that i am really good friends with emily harris again. i love that girl.
i like that i have met amazing people this summer.
i like going to geauga lake and almost flying out of the inner tubes.
i like going on camping trips with some of my favorite people.
i like swimming at orion's house and jumping on his trampoline until the wee hours of the morning.
i like parties that have a room filled with foam.
i like walking around the foam room with bill.
i like playing intense uno championships with mark.
i like being married to george, even when he is abusive.
i like "breaking" into people's residences when they are not home.
i like when people make me birthday cards on post-it notes.
i like working with bryan, joe, brandon, and chris. they make me laugh and make me chicken fingers.
i like being caught sneaking in rachel and trysh at the drive-in. GOOD GOING GUYS.
i like eating at olive garden and getting a discount thanks to orion.
i like getting drunk phone calls from tim betts.
i like driving with my hand on my cd player.
i like when orion and george cook hotdogs and burn them to an absolute crisp. N-DOGS.
i like free mootown ice cream.
i like reading mark durica myspace blogs.
i like making tacos with ashley joe and george.
i like being married to bill lynch. he is nice.
i like getting singing voicemails from mark srsich while i am at work.
i like calling coleman at 1:30 am to find out who sings "sweet caroline".
i like getting phone calls from samuel l. jackson telling me to see snakes on a plane.

and that is all i can think of as of now. this summer has been great. probably my favorite. or one of. 
so thanks trysh

but.... ITS NOT WHAT YOU THINK <3333

love.

i will prove trish wrong.
i will NOT make out with ANYONE next party.
